### IN RANGE
Returns true if the provided date is contained in the provided date_range.

```esql
FROM employees
| WHERE IN_RANGE(hire_date, TO_DATE_RANGE("1985-02-01..1985-03-01"))
| KEEP emp_no, hire_date
| SORT emp_no
```
